orner-all,.ui-corner-bottom,.ui-corner-right,.ui-corner-br{border-bottom-right-radius:4px}.ui-widget-overlay{background:#666 url(images/ui-bg_diagonals-thick_20_666666_40x40.png) 50% 50% repeat;opacity:.5;filter:Alpha(Opacity=50)}.ui-widget-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng du t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u0103n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u1edbi t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Bouygues, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u00e2n Parc des Princes (C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1972.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m m\u1edbi s\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/chum-anh-con-mua-phao-sang-tren-san-hang-day-cua-cdv-hai-phong-291-181826.html\" target=\"_blank\">H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby </span>c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd k\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Boyugues v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i t\u1ea1o to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi 250 tri\u1ec7u Euro (kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n 7 ng\u00e0n t\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ed3ng).\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bau Hien chi khung, quyet lam moi san Hang Day khong kem san PSG hinh anh\" title=\"B\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n chi kh\u1ee7ng, quy\u1ebft l\u00e0m m\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m s\u00e2n PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Ha\u0300ng-Da\u0302\u0303y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o sau khi l\u00e0m m\u1edbi s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u, ph\u00e1c th\u1ea3o v\u00e0 tri\u1ec3n khai x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m c\u00e1c SV\u0110 hi\u1ec7n nay tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Bouygues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng s\u00e2n Parc des Princes (C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed) v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1972. S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n nay c\u1ee7a CLB PSG c\u00f2n l\u00e0 s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eafn v\u00e0o m\u00e1i v\u00f2m. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 EURO 1984, FIFA 1998 v\u00e0 EURO 2016.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 2010, Bouygues c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n d\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p SV\u0110 Velodrome c\u1ee7a Marseille v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 194,14 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a 67 ngh\u00ecn ch\u1ed7 ng\u1ed3i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho EURO 2016.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi uy t\u00edn x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng Trung t\u00e2m H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (n\u0103m 1997) nh\u00e2n d\u1ecbp t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb th\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh Ph\u00e1p ng\u1eef l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 7 v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u Ph\u00fa L\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1ec9nh H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng (n\u0103m 1995), Bouygues \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t g\u1eedi v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00e1c k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u0103ng cai c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\nThanh Long (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-vs-hai-phong-loi-moi-den-voi-cac-khan-dai-vleague-2018-291-181843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/12/ha-noi-vs-hai-phong-loi-moi-den-voi-cac-khan-dai-vleague-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-vs-hai-phong-loi-moi-den-voi-cac-khan-dai-vleague-2018-291-181843.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i V-League 2018 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n ch\u1ea7n ch\u1edd c\u00f3 n\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n xem V-League 2018 hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c...</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"564","checkdouble":"183010"},{"date":"15:08 28/03","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh cay c\u00fa v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 tu\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/nguoi-anh-cay-cu-vi-de-tuot-chien-thang-truoc-y.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px