n:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gareth Southgate ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd.<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Lorenzo Insigne l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m penalty, nh\u01b0ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng d\u1eef d\u1ed9i, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u1ea3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1eafc l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 HLV Gareth Southgate c\u00e0ng th\u00eam l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-184-182952.html\">Anh 1-1 \u00dd</span> trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tam Su chi trich VAR vi qua penalty oan uong tran Anh 1-1 Y hinh anh\" title=\"Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch VAR v\u00ec qu\u1ea3 penalty oan u\u1ed5ng tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/nguoi-anh-cay-cu-vi-de-tuot-chien-thang-truoc-y.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i trong tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u01a1 h\u1ed3, l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e3i nhau c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. VAR th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u00edch trong chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u1ea3, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng. Nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 Lan, \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00ec th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf trong hai ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u201cn\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n\u201d James Tarkowski c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi Federico Chiesa. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Burnley: \u201c\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty. Tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eabm l\u00ean ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec anh ta ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9t nhi\u00ean ng\u00e3 ra khi \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Anh r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 th\u1edf khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm, trong khi nh\u1eefng Panama hay Tunisia \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft g\u1ecdn nh\u1eb9 n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Highlights tr\u1eadn Anh 1-1 \u00dd:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/qhvzg.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia Khoa \u2013 B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h<o:p></o:p></p></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"563","checkdouble":"182994"},{"date":"16:14 28/03","title":"Ronaldinho gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n b\u1ecf MU, ch\u1ecdn Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/ronaldinho-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-bo-mu-chon-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolut