background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, &ldquo;R\u00f4 v\u1ea9u&rdquo; g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch Old Trafford m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou. V\u00ec sao Ronaldinho t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU?<br>\r\n</strong></h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi chia tay David Beckham sau v\u1ee5 &ldquo;chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y bay&rdquo; n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng, HLV huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Sir Alex Ferguson \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o c\u00f4ng cu\u1ed9c t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Ronaldinho &ndash; ng\u00f4i sao khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau s\u1ed1 1, v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf 2 b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong-c187-p1.html\">chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span>.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ec9 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, Barca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u00e0 Ronaldinho t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Camp Nou thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a v\u1ee5 l\u1eadt k\u00e8o n\u00e0y, Ronaldinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/Manchester-United-1.html\">Man United</span>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong 48 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng di\u1ec5n ra, Sandro Rosell \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec7n cho t\u00f4i. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Barca, li\u1ec7u t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Barca ch\u1ee9. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi l\u00e0 c\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldinho tu choi MU, chon Barca trong qua khu\" title=\"Ronaldinho t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, ch\u1ecdn Barca trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/ronaldinho-giai-thich-nguyen-nhan-bo-mu-chon-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ronaldinho t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU, ch\u1ecdn Barca trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf v\u1edbi Man United khi Rosell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea7u c\u1eed. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Barca. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhanh ch\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi M.U r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/barcelona-37.html\">Barcelona</span>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalona, Ronaldinho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, gi\u00e0nh Champions League v\u00e0 La Liga. M\u00f9a h\u00e8 2008, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi AC Milan v\u00e0 khi nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, anh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn&rdquo; &ndash; Ronaldinho cho bi\u1ebft. &ldquo;Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil r\u1ea5t y\u00eau Barca, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf \u0111\u00f3. B\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, kh\u00f4ng n\u01a1i n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u00f3 b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n vui v\u1ebb khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Barcelona.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nh\u1edb Barca. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t CLB v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 lu\u00f4n y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng&rdquo; &ndash; C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Brazil k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Sir Alex Ferguson v\u00e0 Man United c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng m\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n m\u1eebng r\u1ee1 khi Ronaldinho t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU. B\u1edfi trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/cristiano-ronaldo-44953.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-6-bom-tan-duoc-gach-do-o-hang-tien-ve-172-182934.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-nhuong-mu-6-bom-tan-duoc-gach-do-o-hang-tien-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-mu-6-bom-tan-duoc-gach-do-o-hang-tien-ve-172-182934.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU: 6 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7</span><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n, khi Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m m\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"562","checkdouble":"183012"},{"date":"15:00 28/03","title":"Ramos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/ramos-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-huy-diet-cua-tbn-truoc-argentina.PNG","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-inde