nd:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 Sergio Ramos v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Argentina</strong></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\nR\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 La Roja d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos noi gi sau tran Tay Ban Nha vs Argentina hinh anh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Sergio-Ramos-noi-gi-sau-tran-Tay-Ban-Nha-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Argentina tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\nArgentina kh\u00f4ng Messi \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Argentina t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Messi qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano gi\u00fap h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n trong h\u00e0nh\u00a0tr\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-tay-ban-nha-vs-argentina-2h30-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-372-182954.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina</strong></span> khi\u1ebfn HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng, h\u1ecd cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y La Roja \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Sergio Ramos t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0ng trung v\u1ec7 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/sergio-ramos-44967.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Sergio Ramos</strong></span> v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina: \u201cChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ramos phat bieu sau tran Tay Ban Nha vs Argentina\" title=\"Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/ramos-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-huy-diet-cua-tbn-truoc-argentina.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ramos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n duy tr\u00ec s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi Wolrd Cup 2018 kh\u1edfi tranh. T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y\u201d, Ramos ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span> c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho HLV Jorge Sampaoli s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m khi \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Messi trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh: \u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Messi l\u00e0 ai v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu Messi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Video T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/tbn-vs-argentina.MP4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ramos \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/10710-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ramos \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"561","checkdouble":"182996"},{"date":"15:34 28/03","title":"HLV TBN: \"Hy v\u1ecdng Isco s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/hlv-tbn-hy-vong-isco-se-