\u1ed5 khi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Isco l\u1eadp hat-trick, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/toa-sang-o-doi-tuyen-isco-len-tieng-chi-trich-real-madrid-421-182985.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Isco c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</strong></span> sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco lap hat-trick HLV Tay Ban Nha noi gi hinh anh\" title=\"Isco l\u1eadp hat-trick HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/hlv-tbn-hy-vong-isco-se-bung-no-trong-mau-ao-real-madrid.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Isco l\u1eadp hat-trick trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 6-1 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau khi Isco l\u1eadp hat-trick, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o, Isco di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m 10\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/isco-44962.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Isco</strong></span>, gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y cho th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga\u201d, HLV T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Isco kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Zidane tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/real-madrid-29.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Real Madrid</strong></span>, Lopetegui chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, m\u1ed7i HLV c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng Zidane v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u00e0 vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Isco trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/10/Tien-ve-Isco-va-Asensio-bi-canh-bao-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Isco</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina, HLV c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac. T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u00f2n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArgentina r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Messi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean \u1ea3o t\u01b0\u1edfng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp trung, b\u1edfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n\u201d, Lopetegui n\u00f3i th\u00eam.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/103417-42556/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Isco \u1edf La Liga 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Video T\u00e2y Ban Nha 6-1 Argentina (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP