tiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jurgen Klopp v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, Marc Kosicke l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2>Jurgen Klopp l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/huan-luyen-vien/jurgen-klopp-20.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>HLV Jurgen Klopp</strong></span> \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool, \u00f4ng \u0111ang bi\u1ebfn The Kop th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebfn r\u0169. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong Top 3 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Premier League, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nguoi dai dien len tieng ve tuong lai Jurgen Klopp hinh anh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jurgen Klopp h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/10/Nguoi-dai-dien-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-Jurgen-Klopp-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Klopp \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Bayern Munich \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c. Jupp Heynckes s\u1ebd r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a, \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Klopp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBayern tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Bundesliga, Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich. Ngo\u00e0i \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/psg-bat-ngo-muon-co-hlv-cua-liverpool-197-182609.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Klopp</strong></span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay HLV Emery.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV Klopp</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">NHM Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng khi m\u00e0 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jurgen Klopp v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng, Marc Kosicke l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng chia s\u1ebb: \u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022 v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 Klopp s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truoc them Man City vs Liverpool: Matthaus dat niem tin vao Klopp\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m Man City vs Liverpool: Matthaus \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/26/liverpool-co-the-cham-dut-su-thong-tri-cua-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai HLV\u00a0Klopp</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201c<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u00e0nh to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield, s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00f4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi n\u01a1i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Klopp \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Bayern Munich, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ebf\u00a0ho\u1ea1ch tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV c\u1ee7a Bayern hay kh\u00f4ng\u201d, Kosicke ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG, cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Premier League s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace, \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t