{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dele Alli, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam s\u01b0.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dele Alli ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan v\u00e0 Italia, Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan 1-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley, S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Nh\u00ecn chung m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phu nhan mau thuan, HLV Gareth Southgate phat bieu ve Dele Alli hinh anh\" title=\"Ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dele Alli h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/hlv-dt-anh-dam-bao-vi-tri-cho-dele-alli.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Dele Alli ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nC\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong hai tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Dele Alli th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/tottenham-hotspur-5.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> Tottenham </strong></span>kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi H\u00e0 Lan anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong 30 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Italia r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Raheem Sterling, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain thay v\u00ec ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham, vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang lo ng\u1ea1i vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eefa Southgate v\u00e0 Alli c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho Dele Alli</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 nghi ng\u1edd t\u1eeb NHM, HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/dele-alli-54468.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Dele Alli</strong></span>, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Spurs v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam s\u01b0: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 t\u00f4i b\u1ecf r\u01a1i nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u0169 nh\u01b0 Alli ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southgate\" title=\"Southgate\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/2/hlv-southgate-noi-ve-wc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dele Alli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Alli \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alli v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d, HLV Gareth Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Dele Alli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSouthgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/truc-tiep-anh-vs-italia-02h00-ngay-283-giao-huu-quoc-te-184-182952.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Anh vs Italia</strong></span>: \u201cNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, Lingard v\u00e0 Sterling li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Vardy, Lallana c\u0169ng ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n, nh\u00ecn chung t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Anh \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK World Cup 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Dele Alli \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/198028-40942/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Dele Alli \u1edf Premier League 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Video Anh 1-1 Italia (Giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/qhvzg.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"558","checkdouble":"183002"},{"date":"16:34 28/03","title":"Ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, tuy\u1ec3n Anh mang \u01a1n... Pep Guardiola","type":"B\