\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Steve Nicol.</strong></h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</h2>\r\n<h2><strong>Liverpool \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/liverpool-va-real-nhan-tin-mung-vu-thu-mon-cua-roma-180-182742.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool quan t\u00e2m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson</strong></span> c\u1ee7a Roma. The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 30 \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huyen thoai san Anfield muon Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma hinh anh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/20/Huyen-thoai-san-Anfield-muon-Liverpool-mua-Gianluigi-Donnarumma-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Mignolet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Alisson \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Real Madrid n\u1eefa, \u0111\u1ea5y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 Roma mu\u1ed1n 90 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil, \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 Liverpool quan t\u00e2m Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma l\u00e0 do <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/thong-tin-cau-thu/simon-mignolet-44917.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mignolet</strong></span> \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Loris Karius, Napoli \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sunderland, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2><strong>Steve Nicol mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a The Kop, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Steve Nicol mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan: \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karius, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Karius. Liverpool c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 Donnarumma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1ee3p l\u00fd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" title=\"Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/nguoi-cu-muon-liverpool-mua-thu-mon-cua-ac-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nicol mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Gianluigi Donnarumma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn g\u00ec n\u1ebfu Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson c\u1ee7a Roma, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn cho r\u1eb1ng Donnarumma l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Liverpool ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSteve Nicol c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Liverpool</strong></span> \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trung v\u1ec7 Virgil van Dijk v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng: \u201cTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 n\u01a1i y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Liverpool. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Van Dijk \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Donnarumma \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://sja.sportradar.com/w/Bongda24H/756514-42720/033100\">Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gianluigi Donnarumma \u1edf Serie A 2017/18</span></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"556","checkdouble":"183013"},{"date":"12:12 28/03","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-tran-hoa-cua-viet-nam-truoc-jordan.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color: