iclerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1 l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 27/3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> ra s\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Jordan t\u1ea1i l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019. V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i do \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 24 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 s\u1ee5t gi\u1ea3m th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c trong hi\u1ec7p 2 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o to\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t mong manh \u1edf hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi tr\u00e2n h\u00f2a 1-1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Le Thuy Hai danh gia cao DT Viet Nam o tran gap Jordan hinh anh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Jordan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-nhan-xet--dT-Viet-Nam-sau-khi-hoa-Jordan-az4a5982-1522206794-width713height500.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Jordan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y tr\u00ean b\u00e1o D\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t, c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, t\u00ednh k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u r\u1ed3i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Ch\u00fang ta l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u201cc\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi\u201d l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m ra v\u1ec1.</span>\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Jordan, \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i 'l\u01a1' cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cH\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh cao to, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p theo c\u1eb7p t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft th\u00fac qu\u00e1 t\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u k\u00e9m, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t s\u00fat c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u201cNh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ee5c, Jordan ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n ch\u00fang ta, t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n h\u01a1n v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eady l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t r\u1ed3i\u201d, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00e0o l\u00fac 12h00 tr\u01b0a gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbci. Theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i N\u1ed9i B\u00e0i v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai 29/3, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho v\u00f2ng 4<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"> V-League 2018</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Highlight Jordan 1-1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam (V\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup 2019)</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/3/28/Highlight-Jordan-vs-Viet-Nam.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea1nh C\u01b0\u1eddng (B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h)</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/dang-van-lam-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-gap-phai-292-182989.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/dang-van-lam-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-gap-phai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/dang-van-lam-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-gap-phai-292-182989.html\">\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i</span><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Jordan m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1ecdn 90 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"555","checkdouble":"182990"},{"date":"13:29 28/03","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam: L\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i khen th\u1ea7y Park!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/du-am-tran-hoa-cua-viet-nam-lai-phai-khen-thay-park.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer div{top:0;left:0}.closeAdsbt{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px;font-weight:bold}.closeAds{position:absolute;z-index:1000;right:5px;bottom:80px;color:#fff;background-color:#0f0f0f;padding:5px;opacity:.5}.articlerelatepannel{padding:6px;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;background-