1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh  hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Ho\u00e0ng Anh&nbsp;Gia Lai HAGL&nbsp;vs U19 tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 U19 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf b\u00e1o Thanh&nbsp;Ni\u00ean l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y 28/3.</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>LINK XEM ONLINE</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/eP57_Zo7vKA\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\"></iframe> Sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Chonburi (Th\u00e1i Lan) v\u00e0 U19 FC Seoul (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c), \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U19 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 Pleiku, t\u1ec9nh Gia Lai. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh U19 FC Seoul l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ecdn U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Mito Hollyhock (Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n) v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 HAGL JMG. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hai cu\u1ed9c so t\u00e0i s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV V\u0169 H\u1ed3ng Vi\u1ec7t chia s\u1ebb: &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh U19 FC Seoul l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u00ec th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u&quot;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Quan s\u00e1t Mito Hollyhock thi \u0111\u1ea5u, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c U19 FC Seoul. Trong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi U19 Mito Hollyhock. C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 U19 HAGL JMG, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft U19 Qu\u1ed1c gia v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u1ecd</div></div></body></html>","new_url":"","id":"553","checkdouble":"182992"},{"date":"11:18 28/03","title":"Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i \u201cValvelona\u201d l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c cules","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"http://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/28/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules.jpg","new_desc":"<html><head><style type='text/css'>@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Regular.ttf);font-weight:400}@font-face{font-family:MyWebFont;src:url(NotoSans-Bold.ttf);font-weight:700}body{background:#fff;font-family:MyWebFont,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;padding:0;margin:0}iframe a{margin:6px}.clear{clear:both}.clear5px{clear:both;height:10px}img{border:0}h1{margin:6px 0;font-size:24px;color:#f00}h2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}.mnh2{color:#f00;float:left;font-size:16px;margin:0}h3{margin:0}h4{margin:0}div.adContainer video{left:0}.adContainer{position:absolute;left:0;top:0;z-index:2}.jp-video-full div.adContainer d