get-shadow{margin:-5px 0 0 -5px;padding:5px;background:#000 url(images/ui-bg_flat_10_000000_40x100.png) 50% 50% repeat-x;opacity:.2;filter:Alpha(Opacity=20);border-radius:5px}.link-web>a{color:#555;font-size:12px;line-height:24px}body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 18px;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style></head><body><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca th\u1eddi Valverde x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb t\u1ea9y chay. Cules hay Madridistas c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 gi\u1ebft ch\u1ebft c\u1ea3m x\u00fac.</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Bongda24h.vn</strong></span> kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca th\u1eddi Valverde. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, xin vui l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ecdc l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 suy ng\u1eabm.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-loi-choi-real-va-barca-180-182545.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110\u00e2y Real v\u00e0 Bernabeu, kia Barca v\u00e0 Camp Nou&hellip;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho-184-182176.html\">Barca v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Chelsea: B\u1eafn l\u00ean &ldquo;x\u00e1c ch\u1ebft&rdquo;, c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng tung h\u00f4?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/goc-nhin-tu-khi-nao-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-coi-ti-hon-nhu-khong-lo-180-181877.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u1eeb khi n\u00e0o, Barca coi t\u00ed hon nh\u01b0 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/quan-diem-valverde-la-ke-an-may-khong-phai-thien-tai-cua-barca-180-181655.html\">Quan \u0111i\u1ec3m: Valverde l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0103n may, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi\u00ean t\u00e0i c\u1ee7a Barca!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-thang-atletico-2-chu-thuyet-phuc-o-noi-dau-180-181340.html\">Barca th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc Atletico: 2 ch\u1eef &ldquo;thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c&rdquo; \u1edf n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2u?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u: Barca d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 l\u1ea7n b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1: Th\u1ebf n\u00e0o l\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c? Xin th\u01b0a, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea1m tr\u00f9 v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea1m tr\u00f9 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 mu\u1ed1n nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0m n\u00ean truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng Barca. Cule ch\u00e2n ch\u00ednh y\u00eau Barca v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n s\u1eafc, c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch b\u1ec1 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u1eabn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2u. C\u00f2n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng comment ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u00e0 v\u00f4 l\u00fd tr\u00ean <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Bongda24h.vn</strong></span> nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n qua, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 y\u00eau ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi h\u1ecd, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan doi loi choi Barca thoi Valverde la trach nhiem cua cules hinh anh\" title=\"Ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca th\u1eddi Valverde l\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a cules h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/phan-doi-loi-choi-barca-thoi-valverde-la-trach-nhiem-cua-cules.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valverde \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n... ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i sao<strong> </strong><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/barca-vuot-qua-chelsea-ban-len-xac-chet-co-gi-dang-tung-ho-184-182176.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 51, 0);\">l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i Barca th\u1eddi Valverde</span></strong></span> b\u1ecb xem l\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 t\u1ea1i sao c\u00e1c cules c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i &ldquo;Valvelona&rdquo;? \u0110\u00e1p \u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 ngay sau \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Valverde \u0111ang l\u1ea1m quy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1i Barca</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u1eddi n\u00f3i gi\u00f3 bay&rdquo; l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1eadt. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Barcelona, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/quan-diem-valverde-la-ke-an-may-khong-phai-thien-tai-cua-barca-180-181655.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 51, 0);\">Ernesto Valverde</span></strong></span> \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o bao g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu. Khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u CLB, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Athletic Bilbao g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u lia l\u1ecba \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y Valverde nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c, s\u1ebfp Bartomeu th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n nh\u1eafc kh\u00e9o \u00f4ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee9a. &ldquo;Valverde y\u00eau c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 c\u00f3 tri\u1ebft l\u00fd b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u1edbi Barca. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng&rdquo;, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Blaugrana n\u00f3i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2017/18.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Valverde quen sach loi hua voi Bartomeu\" title=\"Valverde quen sach loi hua voi Bartomeu\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Valverde-quen-sach-loi-hua-voi-Bartomeu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca qu\u00ean s\u1ea1ch l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a v\u1edbi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u00fac n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp nghe l\u1ea1i, h\u1eb3n Bartomeu ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ng\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Valverde kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 y\u00eau tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 y\u00eau tri\u1ebft l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca nh\u01b0 \u00f4ng ngh\u0129. Ch\u1ec9 duy nh\u1ea5t Jose Arnaiz l\u00e0 &ldquo;m\u1ea7m non&rdquo; c\u1ee7a l\u00f2 La Masia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Valverde tung ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbn l\u00e0 La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n c\u00f3&hellip; 5 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThay v\u00ec \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb, Valverde &ldquo;b\u1eaft&rdquo; Barca mua v\u1ec1 cho m\u00ecnh h\u1ebft Nelson Semedo, Paulinho, Philippe Coutinho, Ousmade Dembele v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Yerry Mina v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 390 tri\u1ec7u Euro. N\u1ebfu chia trung b\u00ecnh, m\u1ed7i t\u00e2n binh Barca c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 g\u1ea7n 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barca, n\u01a1i c\u00f3 h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n uy t\u00edn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho va Dembele\" title=\"Coutinho va Dembele\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/28/Coutinho-va-Dembele.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valverde t\u1ea1o &quot;bom t\u1ea5n&quot; thay v\u00ec tin d\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ch\u1eebng \u0111\u0